<html><head><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" /><meta http-equiv="Content-Style-Type" content="text/css" /><meta name="generator" content="Aspose.Words for .NET 13.4.0.0" /><title>Minutes of meeting – 10 December 2009</title></head><body><div><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:center"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">Supplementary written evidence from Professional Standards Authority (HCP0010)</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 6pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">A</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">udit </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">of initial stages of fitness to practise </span></p><h1 style="margin:20pt 0pt 12pt 35.45pt; page-break-after:avoid; text-indent:-35.45pt"><span style="display:inline; font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-decoration:none; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline">1.</span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">What is the purpose of the audit?</span></h1><h2 style="font-weight:normal; margin:6pt 0pt 3pt 35.45pt; text-indent:-35.45pt"><span style="display:inline; font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:normal; text-decoration:none; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline">1.1</span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">The Authority</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> seek</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">s</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> assurance that the regulators are protecting patients and the public and maintaining the reputation of the professions and the system of regulation.</span></h2><h2 style="font-weight:normal; margin:6pt 0pt 3pt 35.45pt; text-indent:-35.45pt"><span style="display:inline; font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:normal; text-decoration:none; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline">1.2</span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">We have legal powers to audit. We check that the regulators’ decisions to close cases have not exposed pat</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">ients and service users to unacceptable risks.  </span></h2><h2 style="font-weight:normal; margin:6pt 0pt 3pt 35.45pt; text-indent:-35.45pt"><span style="display:inline; font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:normal; text-decoration:none; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline">1.3</span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">Our powers of audit are limited to looking at individual cases for the purposes of making ‘general reports’ or ‘general recommendations affecting future cases.’</span><a name="_ftnref1"></a><a href="#_ftn1">[1]</a><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> </span></h2><h1 style="margin:20pt 0pt 12pt 35.45pt; page-break-after:avoid; text-indent:-35.45pt"><span style="display:inline; font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-decoration:none; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline">2.</span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">How do</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold"> we carry out the audit</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">?</span></h1><h2 style="font-weight:normal; margin:6pt 0pt 3pt 35.45pt; text-indent:-35.45pt"><span style="display:inline; font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:normal; text-decoration:none; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline">2.1</span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">We involved p</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">atients, regulators and other stakeholders in developing our audit process. </span></h2><ol type="1" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:normal; margin:6pt 0pt 3pt 50pt; padding-left:4pt; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">We select up to 100 cases closed prior to them going to a final FTP hearing. Some of these cases are picked at random and some are picked based on risk.</span></li><li style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:normal; margin:6pt 0pt 3pt 50pt; padding-left:4pt; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">We check that each case me</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">ets the standards of the ‘Casework</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> Framework</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">’</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> (see section 4).</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> The Casework Framework was agreed based on a consensus view about the key elements that should be found in any good casework system that is focused on protecting the public. </span></li><li style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:normal; margin:6pt 0pt 3pt 50pt; padding-left:4pt; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">We provide a table</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> of feedback to the regulator. Examples of what we might feedback include: </span></li></ol><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 6pt 78pt; text-indent:-21.3pt"><span style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:12pt"></span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">Failure to fully investigate before closing a case</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 6pt 78pt; text-indent:-21.3pt"><span style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:12pt"></span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">Delays in case handling</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 6pt 78pt; text-indent:-21.3pt"><span style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:12pt"></span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">Providing inadequate reasons for a decision</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">.</span></p><ol start="4" type="1" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:normal; margin:6pt 0pt 3pt 50pt; padding-left:4pt; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">Once the regulator has commented on our feedback, we draft t</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">he report. In the report we will draw conclusions on the findings</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">. Examples include: </span></li></ol><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 6pt 78pt; text-indent:-21.3pt"><span style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:12pt"></span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">Weaknesses in infrastructure </span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 6pt 78pt; text-indent:-21.3pt"><span style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:12pt"></span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">Effectiveness of management controls</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">.</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">  </span></p><h2 style="font-weight:normal; margin:6pt 0pt 3pt 35.45pt; text-indent:-35.45pt"><span style="display:inline; font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:normal; text-decoration:none; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline">2.2</span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">Once the report is agreed we share the report with the </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">Department of </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">H</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">ealth</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> in England, </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">the Governments in Scotland, Wales </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">and </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">Northern Ireland</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> and the Health Committee</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">. We publish the report on our website.  </span></h2><h1 style="margin:20pt 0pt 12pt 35.45pt; page-break-after:avoid; text-indent:-35.45pt"><span style="display:inline; font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-decoration:none; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline">3.</span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">The</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">2013 </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">audit</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">s</span></h1><h2 style="font-weight:normal; margin:6pt 0pt 3pt 35.45pt; text-indent:-35.45pt"><span style="display:inline; font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:normal; text-decoration:none; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline">3.1</span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">2013 was the final year in our first three-year cycle of risk-based auditing.</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> We audited the following regulators: </span></h2><ul type="disc" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="color:#7f1399; font-family:Symbol; font-size:12pt; margin:0pt 0pt 6pt 45.97pt; padding-left:10.73pt